Ron, the Singing Dogs have been in every machine every Christmas, whether t=
he location owner likes it or not, since each installation was made.

I remember in fall 1988 the first Christmas for this location here on the e=
ast side. When i played the dogs right after putting them in, two of the Me=
xican workers stopped in their tracks and listened with a contemplative loo=
k on their faces.=A0 Rufuvio said "perros!"=A0 I cruelly broke the spell by=
 saying "anyone you know?"

That and the Chipmunks are the first things they ask about each year.

i love Mexicans.

Rob

